      "id": "PopularPost159012",
      "post_content": "In Revised rulebook it was clearly stated that all cost:+x/+y effects wear off at the end of the turn. I still think that effects are not permanent unless the card says so. So first time I saw [Stalking Stones](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stalking Stones) I thought that's crap, pay six mana to get a 3/3 land creature for a turn.",
      "posted_by": "tavaritz",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost159012\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">In Revised rulebook it was clearly stated that all cost:+x/+y effects wear off at the end of the turn. I still think that effects are not permanent unless the card says so. So first time I saw <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stalking Stones\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stalking Stones\">Stalking Stones</a> I thought that's crap, pay six mana to get a 3/3 land creature for a turn.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '159012'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy58371\">tavaritz</span>\r\n                                (5/8/2011 3:20:51 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/S