    {
      "id": "PopularPost109950",
      "post_content": "Fourth edition cleaned up the wording on a lot of auras, though Holy Armor never caused that much confusion. It was simply understood that the pumpable bonuses provided by the Armor were temporary, much like the bonuses provided by [Firebreathing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Firebreathing) or [Atog](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Atog)'s ability. Back then, if it didn't say \"permanently,\" you had to assume it wasn't. Then again, the +0/+2 bonus provided by the Armor *is* permanent, and it doesn't mention that. As I read the card now, it seems way more confusing than it ever did back in 1994. WotC's rigid wording has killed my ability to reason deductively!",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost109950\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Fourth edition cleaned up the wording on a lot of auras, though Holy Armor never caused that much confusion.  It was simply understood that the pumpable bonuses provided by the Armor were temporary, much like the bonuses provided by <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Firebreathing\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Firebreathing\">Firebreathing</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Atog\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Atog\">Atog</a>'s ability.  Back then, if it didn't say \"permanently,\" you had to assume it wasn't.  Then again, the +0/+2 bonus provided by the Armor <i>is</i> permanent, and it doesn't mention that.  As I read the card now, it seems way more confusing than it ever did back in 1994.  WotC's rigid wording has killed my ability to reason deductively!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '109950'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (10/14/2010 8:05:48 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </